id: pm-yf8t
title: "Fix Auto Release failure: build dist before pm-changelog generation runs"
description: "The Auto Release workflow (.github/workflows/auto-release.yml) installs deps then immediately runs scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs, which (after the pm-changelog integration in commits b219aeed/4345920c) calls 'node dist/cli.js install npm:pm-changelog --project' and 'node dist/cli.js changelog generate ...' before any build runs. dist/cli.js does not exist at that point (runReleaseGates builds, but that runs AFTER the changelog step), so the run fails with 'Cannot find module .../dist/cli.js'. Daily auto-release has failed since 2026-05-24 (runs 26353906615, 26387640606). Other workflows (ci.yml:73, nightly.yml:80, release.yml) all run 'pnpm build' first; auto-release.yml is the only one missing it. Fix: add a Build step to auto-release.yml before the pipeline, and add a regression contract test asserting the build precedes the pipeline invocation. pm-changelog package itself is fine (v2026.5.24-15; local changelog:pm:check passes, 825 items, unchanged)."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[5]: changelog,ci,pm-changelog,release,reliability
created_at: "2026-05-25T08:18:53.175Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-25T08:56:50.697Z"
assignee: claude-code-agent
author: claude-code-agent
parent: pm-rnpb
comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-25T08:20:11.943Z",release-ci-subagent,"release-ci-subagent START: Plan = (1) add a 'Build' step (run: pnpm build) to .github/workflows/auto-release.yml between 'Install dependencies' and 'Run auto release pipeline' so dist/cli.js exists before run-release-pipeline.mjs calls it for pm-changelog generation; (2) add a regression contract test in tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts asserting auto-release.yml contains 'pnpm build' AND that its indexOf precedes run-release-pipeline.mjs; (3) run the contract spec. Not touching CHANGELOG.md, config.ts, or run-release-pipeline.mjs."
  "2026-05-25T08:20:41.641Z",release-ci-subagent,"release-ci-subagent DONE.\n\nFILES CHANGED (2):\n1) .github/workflows/auto-release.yml -- inserted a new step between 'Install dependencies' and 'Run auto release pipeline':\n      - name: Build\n        run: pnpm build\n   This builds dist/cli.js so the release pipeline (run-release-pipeline.mjs lines ~284-302) can call 'dist/cli.js install npm:pm-changelog --project' and 'dist/cli.js changelog generate' without Cannot-find-module errors. Verified step order is now Install dependencies -> Build -> Run auto release pipeline; YAML parses cleanly.\n\n2) tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts -- added regression test 'builds dist before the auto-release pipeline consumes dist/cli.js' (placed right after the existing auto-release workflow contract test). It reads auto-release.yml, asserts it contains 'pnpm build', and asserts indexOf('pnpm build') < indexOf('scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs') so the build always precedes the pipeline. Matches existing indexOf style in the file.\n\nTESTS RUN:\n  node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts\n  => 1 file passed, 11 tests passed (was 10, +1 new). Build runs first then tests; all green.\n\nNOT TOUCHED (per constraints): CHANGELOG.md, src/cli/commands/config.ts (other agent), scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs (workflow-only fix is sufficient; pipeline assumes dist/cli.js exists, which is the correct contract for a release job).\n\nCOORDINATOR TODO:\n  - Add CHANGELOG.md [Unreleased] line, e.g. under Fixed:\n    'Fixed daily Auto Release workflow failing since 2026-05-24 by adding the missing pnpm build step before the release pipeline, so dist/cli.js exists when pm-changelog generation runs (pm-yf8t).'\n  - Do NOT close pm-yf8t until PR merges (per instructions)."
  "2026-05-25T08:40:50.850Z",codex-gh-triage,"GitHub triage addendum 2026-05-25: latest Auto Release failure confirmed in gh run 26387640606 on main c036f238. Job installs dependencies, does not run build, then run-release-pipeline prints v2026.5.25 and fails at node dist/cli.js install npm:pm-changelog --project with MODULE_NOT_FOUND for dist/cli.js. This matches the item description; recommended fix remains adding pnpm build before the pipeline and keeping the workflow-order regression test."
  "2026-05-25T08:41:02.478Z",codex-impl-review,"Implementation-review evidence: reviewed current uncommitted auto-release diff only. .github/workflows/auto-release.yml now runs pnpm build before scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs; release-automation contract covers that order. Verified with node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/config-positional-value.spec.ts tests/unit/config-command.spec.ts tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts (3 files, 55 tests passed). No blocking auto-release findings."
  "2026-05-25T08:56:50.697Z",codex-dedupe-agent,"Coordinator verification: auto-release build ordering fix is bundled in this PR. Regression test covers pnpm build before run-release-pipeline; full release gate passed after the branch changes. pm-changelog latest installed as 2026.5.24-15 and CHANGELOG.md check is unchanged."
body: ""
